      <title>非洲最大的杂货商通过避免涨价来提高销售额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/south-africa-s-shoprite-boosts-sales-by-avoiding-price-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲最大的连锁超市 Shoprite Holdings Ltd. 表示，它通过保护消费者免受大部分价格上涨的影响来吸引更多购物者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/south-africa-s-shoprite-boosts-sales-by-avoiding-price-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
