      <title>Spark称塔塔之子IPO估值高达960亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/tata-sons-may-be-valued-at-up-to-96-billion-in-ipo-spark-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于孟买的投资银行公司 Spark PWM Pvt. 表示，塔塔儿子有限公司 (Tata Sons Ltd.) 在未来 18 个月内可能进行的首次公开募股中，估值可能高达 8 万亿卢比（960 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/tata-sons-may-be-valued-at-up-to-96-billion-in-ipo-spark-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:26:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车因保时捷电动汽车电池引发船舶火灾而面临两起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/volkswagen-faces-lawsuits-over-claim-porsche-ev-battery-sparked-ship-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车公司在德国面临两起诉讼，据称是保时捷电动汽车的电池引发了 2022 年一艘大型货船的火灾，最终导致船上数千辆汽车沉没。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/volkswagen-faces-lawsuits-over-claim-porsche-ev-battery-sparked-ship-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:08:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜耳承诺解决利润进一步下降的问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/bayer-forecasts-another-year-of-falling-profit-keeps-structure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜耳公司预计今年利润将再次下降，并选择暂时坚持其集团结构，因为该公司正在努力克服威胁公司长期未来的数十亿美元的法律困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/bayer-forecasts-another-year-of-falling-profit-keeps-structure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:40:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚总理普拉博沃誓言加快经济增长和财政纪律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/indonesia-s-prabowo-seeks-faster-growth-vows-fiscal-discipline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚国防部长普拉博沃·苏比安托(Prabowo Subianto)在上个月的总统选举中获胜，他表示，一旦就任总统，他将坚持财政审慎，并保持经济稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/indonesia-s-prabowo-seeks-faster-growth-vows-fiscal-discipline</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:11:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ETF 成交量飙升，中国股市午后延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/chinese-stocks-decline-as-2024-growth-target-fails-to-impress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些追踪中国股票的交易所交易基金成交量激增，这表明在一些投资者对政府的增长目标表示失望后，国家支持的基金正在支撑市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/chinese-stocks-decline-as-2024-growth-target-fails-to-impress</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 01:58:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着焦点从中国转向鲍威尔，股市下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场对中国建立经济信心的新目标和措施反应冷淡，且投资者期待美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的证词，股市小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 23:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通认为美国股市存在“泡沫”，而高盛则表示反弹是合理的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/jpmorgan-sees-froth-in-us-stocks-goldman-says-rally-justified</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年美股的大幅上涨让摩根大通的策略师们感到担忧。公司和高盛集团对于市场泡沫是否正在形成存在分歧。]]></description>
